### Prep
- Drain the canned beats of water
- Drain the canned mandarins of water

### Steps
1. Put the spinach into the bowl
2. Add remaining ingredients
3. Toss together
4. Serve

#### To make Oven-Roasted Beet Spinach Salad
1. Preheat oven to 450
2. Remove beet greens from 3 fresh beats
3. Wrap tightly in foil
4. Bake for 40 to 50 minutes
    - Or until tender when pierced 
5. Unwrap the foil
6. Remove the skin by rubbing firmly with paper towels.
7. Slice
8. Add to salad
